I am so excited about not having to worry about this anymore, so excited to have just my own place even if its a mattress on a floor, inside an apartment. Taking showers whenever, not stressing about not being able to eat.

I havent had a real meal for few days and I always try to live on as little as possible as I dont want to leech off of others. Words cannot describe how excited I am about being able to eat next month whenever I am hungry.

